    <fr:p>The Wednesday Seminars are the <fr:link href="camcl.xml" title="Cambridge Computer Laboratory" addr="camcl" type="local">Department</fr:link>’s main seminar series.</fr:p>
    <fr:p>The talks are given by distinguished external speakers as well as members of the department. They are targeted at anyone with a background in computing, but students in particular. Topics span the full range of computer science and beyond.</fr:p>
